Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.57,0:01:20.72,EN-op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}I've been ignoring everyone
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.72,0:01:23.02,EN-op,,0,0,0,,I've been wandering around
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.02,0:01:27.42,EN-op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}I've been deceived everything. At that time
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.78,0:01:32.47,EN-op,,0,0,0,,Then you appeared in front of me. You ignited my pale heart
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.49,0:01:36.77,EN-op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)}We've been looking for each other from now on
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.79,0:01:37.98,EN-op,,0,0,0,,Save you
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.13,0:01:43.57,JP-op,,0,0,0,,際限ない犠牲を
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.05,0:01:48.95,JP-op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}朦朧とした理想を
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.72,0:01:52.70,JP-op,,0,0,0,,もう無駄にしないようにと
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.70,0:01:57.32,JP-op,,0,0,0,,悲しみを切り刻んだ
Dialogue: 1,0:01:58.02,0:02:00.34,EN-op,,0,0,0,,Get away from me
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.34,0:02:03.57,EN-op,,0,0,0,,{\an1}Get away from dark nightmare
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.74,0:02:07.76,EN-op,,0,0,0,,Just now. Chip at your heart. We just fight for freedom
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.89,0:02:12.47,JP-op,,0,0,0,,奪い合って　汚し合って
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.47,0:02:16.66,JP-op,,0,0,0,,それでも守りたくて
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.83,0:02:19.06,EN-op,,0,0,0,,Get away from me
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.06,0:02:22.52,EN-op,,0,0,0,,Get away from dark nightmare
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.53,0:02:27.03,EN-op,,0,0,0,,{\an1}We don't want to go through that again
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.03,0:02:32.60,JP-op,,0,0,0,,{\an1}時は満ちた　始まりの鐘が鳴る
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.56,0:02:39.63,EN-op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1500)}Get away from me
